      • initialize

        public static void initialize(InPlayer.Configuration configuration)

        Authenticates this client as belonging to your application. This must be called before your application can use the InPlayer SDK . The recommended way is to put a call to InPlayer.initialize in your Application's onCreate method:

        public class MyApplication extends Application { public void onCreate() { InPlayer.initialize(configuration); } }

        Parameters:
        configuration - org.jetbrains.dokka.NodeRenderContent@553eea9f: The configuration for your application.
